{
  "id": "6a2413b31ee5b086fe43dc7c",
  "title": "Day Of The Devs: Summer Game Fest Edition 2026",
  "created": 1780749245,
  "updated": 1780755606,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2413b31ee5b086fe43dc7c",
      "text": "Day Of The Devs: Summer Game Fest Edition 2026",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749245,
      "updated": 1780749251
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2413c5000000000094e620",
      "text": "[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eJJ58aEy1-k]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749254,
      "updated": 1780749254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2416fa000000000094e633",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750074,
      "updated": 1780750074
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2413c5000000000094e621",
      "text": "[Day of the Devs] Summer Game Fest Edition 2026を見る",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749254,
      "updated": 1780749273
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2413d9000000000094e622",
      "text": " リアタイはできなかった",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749273,
      "updated": 1780749283
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2413e3000000000094e626",
      "text": " [Tim Schafer]さん[Double Fine]のTシャツだ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749283,
      "updated": 1780749551
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2427fa000000000094e6c0",
      "text": " \tこれ何かの元ネタをGrim Fandangoっぽくアレンジしたやつなのかな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754427,
      "updated": 1780754545
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242851000000000094e6c1",
      "text": " \t2HBというキャラらしい　知らんかった",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754514,
      "updated": 1780754529
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241420000000000094e627",
      "text": " イントロがありえないくらいしょうもない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749344,
      "updated": 1780749383
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2414f9000000000094e62c",
      "text": "\tBlood Dungeon めっちゃおもろそう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749562,
      "updated": 1780749835
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24142d000000000094e628",
      "text": "\t\tMesshofはニーズヘッグとWheel Worldのデベロッパーか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749383,
      "updated": 1780749567
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2414ab000000000094e629",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/a84a584be07f1ffa5406261008c4de66]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749483,
      "updated": 1780749484
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2414ab000000000094e62a",
      "text": "\t\t本棚が気になる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749484,
      "updated": 1780749488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2414af000000000094e62b",
      "text": "\tTenebris Somnia",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749488,
      "updated": 1780749925
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2413c2000000000094e61f",
      "text": "\t\tこれすご！！！めっちゃいいな～",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749251,
      "updated": 1780749829
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2415eb000000000094e62e",
      "text": "\t\tFaith的な8ビットホラーに実写のカットシーンを組み合わせている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749803,
      "updated": 1780749973
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24167a000000000094e630",
      "text": "\t\tあ、Faithの影響だって言った",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749946,
      "updated": 1780750028
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2416cc000000000094e632",
      "text": "\tMr. Records",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750029,
      "updated": 1780750137
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241739000000000094e634",
      "text": "\t\t非常に絵がかわいい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750138,
      "updated": 1780750141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24173c000000000094e635",
      "text": "\t\t[リズムハンター ハーモナイト]を思い出す",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750141,
      "updated": 1780750154
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24175f000000000094e636",
      "text": "\t\tTenebris Somniaもだけど収録なり開発の風景を出してくれるのがめっちゃいいんだよね～～ この番組",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750175,
      "updated": 1780750224
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241822000000000094e63c",
      "text": "\t33 Imortalsはずっとベータテストやってたやつだ。Thunder Lotusだったのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750371,
      "updated": 1780750371
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2417a5000000000094e637",
      "text": "\t\t見てみると確かにSpiritfarerと絵柄がよく似ている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750246,
      "updated": 1780750372
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2418cc000000000094e641",
      "text": "\tDREADMOOR",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750541,
      "updated": 1780750549
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241896000000000094e63d",
      "text": "\t\tめっちゃリッチなDREDGEみたいなやつがきた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750487,
      "updated": 1780750550
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2418bf000000000094e63e",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/1205d4f4aeff7786316253e49106cb5d]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750528,
      "updated": 1780750530
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2418c2000000000094e640",
      "text": " \tクラフト画面がめっちゃわくわくする感じだ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750530,
      "updated": 1780750538
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2418fe000000000094e642",
      "text": " Threads of Time",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750591,
      "updated": 1780750902
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24191a000000000094e646",
      "text": " \tカナダ製クロノトリガー風JRPG",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750619,
      "updated": 1780755058
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241903000000000094e643",
      "text": " \tこのアートスタイルはどこから影響を受けているのだろう。HD-2Dといえばそうなんだがモバイルゲームっぽくもあるかも",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750595,
      "updated": 1780750883
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241a6c000000000094e64e",
      "text": " N PLUS INFINITY TIMES TWO",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750957,
      "updated": 1780751117
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241b0d000000000094e64f",
      "text": " \tなんか見たことあるシリーズのやつだ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751118,
      "updated": 1780751125
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241b15000000000094e650",
      "text": " \t絶対楽しいやつ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751125,
      "updated": 1780755049
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241a0e000000000094e648",
      "text": " \t日本語の本も見える",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750863,
      "updated": 1780750956
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2418c0000000000094e63f",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/1fec82fe0c4ce4a53692ea330c150f27]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750528,
      "updated": 1780750951
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241b31000000000094e652",
      "text": " Into the unwell",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751154,
      "updated": 1780751252
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241a65000000000094e64d",
      "text": "\t\tMOUSE以降こういう3Dかつレトロカートゥーンぽい表現増えたよね",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780750950,
      "updated": 1780751269
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241bd2000000000094e654",
      "text": " \t\t[ラバーホースアニメーション]っていうのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751314,
      "updated": 1780751323
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241c2c000000000094e656",
      "text": " \t\tこのゲームでもビヨンビヨン感がよく出ている めっちゃ滑らかだ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751405,
      "updated": 1780751660
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241b9b000000000094e653",
      "text": "\t\t音楽のスタイルとビジュアルのスタイルがなぜこう交わったのか経緯を推測しづらい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751259,
      "updated": 1780751396
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241c24000000000094e655",
      "text": "\tBub",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751397,
      "updated": 1780751480
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24157b000000000094e62d",
      "text": "\t\tUnity製だと右下にMade with Unityって出るのか　だいぶんでかく出るな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780749692,
      "updated": 1780751445
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241c6b000000000094e659",
      "text": "\t\tこれぞインディーゲームという感じの作品だ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751467,
      "updated": 1780751467
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241ce3000000000094e65b",
      "text": "\t\t素晴らしい紹介だった",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751588,
      "updated": 1780751604
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241d21000000000094e65c",
      "text": "\t\t楽しみ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751649,
      "updated": 1780751650
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241d22000000000094e65d",
      "text": "\tLazy River",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751650,
      "updated": 1780751699
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241d55000000000094e660",
      "text": "\t\tウォーターパークテーマのL4D風バカゲーか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751701,
      "updated": 1780751807
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241df7000000000094e666",
      "text": "\t\tこういうプールのリゾートとか思い出せないくらい行っていない。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751863,
      "updated": 1780751904
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241e0b000000000094e667",
      "text": " \t\t海のある地域に住んでいたからかも。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751883,
      "updated": 1780751898
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241dbf000000000094e663",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/1e6eea77239d80e2d55f32e272a441c6]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751807,
      "updated": 1780751821
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241dcc000000000094e664",
      "text": "\t\t[藤棚]っぽいところで撮影している　良いな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751821,
      "updated": 1780753060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241dd8000000000094e665",
      "text": "\t\t海外にも藤棚はあるのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751833,
      "updated": 1780751836
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242a870000000000d12ba6",
      "text": "\t\tMike Boxleiterさん元ボドゲ開発者らしい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755079,
      "updated": 1780755079
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241db5000000000094e662",
      "text": "\t[Prove You're Human]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751797,
      "updated": 1780751947
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241e4b000000000094e668",
      "text": "\t\tタイトルからまずよさそ！！",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751947,
      "updated": 1780751977
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241e62000000000094e669",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/3769e53243733adc98f69c5d93095600]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751971,
      "updated": 1780751971
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241e63000000000094e66a",
      "text": " \t\tわお　わーお",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751971,
      "updated": 1780751984
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242a8b0000000000d12ba7",
      "text": " \t\tどっちも買ってやってない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755084,
      "updated": 1780755087
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241efe000000000094e670",
      "text": " \t[CAPTCHA]に関する話らしい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752127,
      "updated": 1780752127
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241e70000000000094e66c",
      "text": " \t良さそう過ぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780751985,
      "updated": 1780752087
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241ed6000000000094e66e",
      "text": " ITHACA",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752087,
      "updated": 1780752203
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241fa3000000000094e671",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/a8e2cb7e0482bf3de8f139063d66107f]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752291,
      "updated": 1780752596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241fa3000000000094e672",
      "text": "\t\t景色良すぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752292,
      "updated": 1780752359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a241ffd000000000094e674",
      "text": "\tScreenbound",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752382,
      "updated": 1780752385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242001000000000094e676",
      "text": "\t\tついに形になってきてた　Screenshot Saturdayの一発ネタみたいなやつだったはずだがものすごい練り込まれている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752385,
      "updated": 1780752553
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242094000000000094e678",
      "text": "\t\tカセットふーってやる演出凄いな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752532,
      "updated": 1780752541
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2420f1000000000094e682",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/766b0746fc0fafd5d3fc2d1a9908bb1b]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752626,
      "updated": 1780752626
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2420f1000000000094e683",
      "text": "\t\t血と汗とピクセルがある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752626,
      "updated": 1780752669
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242163000000000094e684",
      "text": "\t\t知らん本をGeminiでしらべた。一番上のディックの下からめっちゃマニアックだ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752740,
      "updated": 1780752772
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242194000000000094e685",
      "text": "\t\t\t『Hey! Listen!』Steve McNeil",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752789,
      "updated": 1780752811
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421a0000000000094e688",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tタイトルは『ゼルダの伝説』の妖精ナビィのセリフから。1970年代から90年代後半までの「ビデオゲーム黄金期」の歴史と裏話を、イギリスのコメディアンである著者がユーモアたっぷりに綴った一冊です。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752801,
      "updated": 1780752814
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242aa80000000000d12ba8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t面白そう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755113,
      "updated": 1780755114
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421a0000000000094e68a",
      "text": "\t\t\t『The Book of Elsewhere』Keanu Reeves / China Miéville",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752801,
      "updated": 1780752824
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421a0000000000094e68d",
      "text": "\t\t\t 俳優キアヌ・リーブスが原案・原作を手がけたコミック『BRZRKR』の世界をベースに、SF・ファンタジー界の鬼才チャイナ・ミエヴィルと奇跡のタッグを組んで書き下ろした、8万年を生きる不死の戦士を巡る重厚なSF小説です。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752801,
      "updated": 1780752828
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421cc000000000094e693",
      "text": "\t\t\t キアヌリーブスのコミックあったなー",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752844,
      "updated": 1780752859
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421a0000000000094e68f",
      "text": "\t\t 『Lord of Blackthorne』Jason Kingsley",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752801,
      "updated": 1780752837
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421a0000000000094e692",
      "text": "\t\t\t 歴史系YouTubeチャンネル「Modern History TV」の主催者であり、ゲーム開発会社 Rebellion のCEOでもある著者によるファンタジー小説です。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752801,
      "updated": 1780752839
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242adb0000000000d12ba9",
      "text": "\t\t\t Rebellionはスナイパーエリートの所か",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755164,
      "updated": 1780755170
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242b1b0000000000d12baa",
      "text": "\t\t\tこの下3冊の著者はイギリス人だった。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755228,
      "updated": 1780755237
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2421e1000000000094e694",
      "text": "\tShot One Fighters",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752866,
      "updated": 1780752896
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242215000000000094e695",
      "text": "\t\tヒットストップのリズム感すごいな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780752917,
      "updated": 1780752921
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242283000000000094e696",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/3045b971432cfc684d0726b166134019]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753028,
      "updated": 1780753029
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242b3b0000000000d12bab",
      "text": " \t\tあんまわからんけどオタク過ぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755260,
      "updated": 1780755314
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242b5e0000000000d12bac",
      "text": " \t\t右側上から2段目のOrdinary って流行りのスキンケア製品だったはず　カオス　カロリーメイトはMGSかな…",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755295,
      "updated": 1780755350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242c720000000000d12baf",
      "text": " \t\t右下ソニック3って映画のグッズっぽいな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755570,
      "updated": 1780755579
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242c820000000000d12bb0",
      "text": "  \t\t調べたらマクドのハッピーセットの箱らしい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780755587,
      "updated": 1780755606
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242294000000000094e698",
      "text": "\tApple Crumble",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753045,
      "updated": 1780753079
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2422fb000000000094e699",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/a1a522bd5712bf2e8b98210330642cef]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753148,
      "updated": 1780753149
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24233f000000000094e69c",
      "text": "\t\t近くにロケできる池があるのが羨ましい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753216,
      "updated": 1780753225
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242306000000000094e69b",
      "text": "\t\tああ！Duck Detectiveのデベロッパか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753159,
      "updated": 1780753183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24236b000000000094e69d",
      "text": "\t\tナイブスアウトの影響について言及している",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753259,
      "updated": 1780753328
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2423bc000000000094e69e",
      "text": "\t\tユーモアたっぷりでよい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753341,
      "updated": 1780753345
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2423c1000000000094e69f",
      "text": "\t\tなんとなくTangle Towerを思い出した。Tangle Towerの新作まだデモ出たっきりだよね",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753345,
      "updated": 1780753445
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242284000000000094e697",
      "text": " Slap out of It!",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753029,
      "updated": 1780753460
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24245d000000000094e6a0",
      "text": " \tわろた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753502,
      "updated": 1780753505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242460000000000094e6a1",
      "text": " \tAnger Footってあったよね。それの手バージョンだ いやFPSで手が出てるのは普通なんだけど",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753505,
      "updated": 1780753555
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242502000000000094e6a3",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/af6c1bee307ad65a81ed6f558c857ae8]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753666,
      "updated": 1780753667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242502000000000094e6a4",
      "text": "\t\tw",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753667,
      "updated": 1780753668
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242505000000000094e6a5",
      "text": "\tSuper Yooka-Laylee Kart",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753670,
      "updated": 1780753712
    },
    {
      "id": "6a24252f000000000094e6a6",
      "text": "\t\t！？！？wwww",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753712,
      "updated": 1780753713
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2425ab000000000094e6ae",
      "text": "\t\tユーカレイリーってそんなにキャラいたっけ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753835,
      "updated": 1780753835
    },
    {
      "id": "6a242551000000000094e6ac",
      "text": "\t\tなんとなく向かって右の人がユーカレイリーのラスボスっぽい風貌をしている…",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753745,
      "updated": 1780753763
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2425df000000000094e6af",
      "text": "\tInto the Fire",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780753888,
      "updated": 1780754027
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2426b4000000000094e6b0",
      "text": "\t\t防災がここまでフィーチャーされるのも珍しいかも",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754101,
      "updated": 1780754117
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2426c5000000000094e6b1",
      "text": "\tTrine 6",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754118,
      "updated": 1780754131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2426d2000000000094e6b2",
      "text": "\t\t6まで出てるのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754131,
      "updated": 1780754135
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2426f0000000000094e6b3",
      "text": "\tWhen Sirens Fall Slient",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754161,
      "updated": 1780754161
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2427af000000000094e6b7",
      "text": "\t\tアイテムがめっちゃ凝ってる　他にも色々タイトルあるけど",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754352,
      "updated": 1780754362
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2427c9000000000094e6bf",
      "text": "\t\tグッチのバッグからゴム散らばってるのとかミッケ的な見てて楽しさがあった",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754377,
      "updated": 1780754382
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2426fc000000000094e6b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780754173,
      "updated": 1780754173
    },
